♫ The broken promises ♫

274
00:20:52,250 --> 00:20:55,660
♫ But you're my light ♫

275
00:20:55,660 --> 00:21:00,150
♫ Just need your care and love ♫

276
00:21:00,150 --> 00:21:04,060
♫ To fill in all my vacancies ♫

277
00:21:09,170 --> 00:21:12,470
In-law, on another day, when you are free, come to my place and try some of my cooking.

278
00:21:12,470 --> 00:21:15,110
All right! I'll definitely be there.

279
00:21:16,040 --> 00:21:19,050
Qiao, congratulations! Congratulations!

280
00:21:19,050 --> 00:21:23,638
- You are so handsome.
- Nian Nian, this one is more handsome than the last one.

281
00:21:24,340 --> 00:21:25,430
Well done.

282
00:21:25,430 --> 00:21:27,470
- Well done, well done.
- Well done.

283
00:21:27,470 --> 00:21:29,840
Please, come inside. Come inside.

284
00:21:32,040 --> 00:21:35,940
Should I feel happy or upset?

285
00:21:35,940 --> 00:21:38,090
You tell me!

286
00:21:39,220 --> 00:21:41,240
Stop eating, In-law!

287
00:21:41,240 --> 00:21:43,670
Do you still want to take care of your grandchildren?

288
00:21:43,670 --> 00:21:46,102
I'll share it with them.

289
00:21:52,350 --> 00:21:54,990
Loosen up your smile to look more natural.

290
00:21:56,740 --> 00:21:58,770
Why have you returned to your old self all of a sudden?

291
00:21:58,770 --> 00:22:00,570
Your acting was pretty good before, wasn't it?

292
00:22:00,570 --> 00:22:03,580
I'm not acting. I'm nervous.

293
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:08,840
Okay, fine. You are too normal now, I'm not quite used to it.

294
00:22:14,290 --> 00:22:15,990
Why are you here?

295
00:22:15,990 --> 00:22:18,100
To take the bride.

296
00:22:18,100 --> 00:22:20,238
Mr. Qiao, he's joking.

297
00:22:20,240 --> 00:22:22,690
Su Nian asked Yunduan to take photos for the wedding. I'm his assistant.

298
00:22:22,690 --> 00:22:24,290
Congratulations to you both.

299
00:22:27,290 --> 00:22:30,240
The ceremony begins in 10 minutes.

300
00:22:34,490 --> 00:22:36,040
You are a human being now

301
00:22:36,040 --> 00:22:38,763
and a happy man at that.

302
00:22:38,763 --> 00:22:42,840
The part where you welcome the guests is over.
Now change your clothes and go see your wife.

303
00:23:27,320 --> 00:23:30,740
In-law, keep an eye open for me too if you can.

304
00:23:30,740 --> 00:23:34,140
I also want to experience love in the twilight years.

305
00:23:35,860 --> 00:23:37,460
[Su Nian]

306
00:23:38,158 --> 00:23:39,938
The day we graduated from high school,

307
00:23:39,940 --> 00:23:41,990
this love letter encountered an accident.

308
00:23:41,990 --> 00:23:44,690
Now, I would like to give it to you again.

309
00:23:52,630 --> 00:23:54,040
Su Nian,

310
00:23:54,040 --> 00:23:56,740
I don't know why I'm writing this letter.

311
00:23:56,740 --> 00:23:59,740
I just know that I feel pain when I see you.

312
00:23:59,740 --> 00:24:03,180
I feel pain when I see you unable to buy the things you want.

313
00:24:03,180 --> 00:24:05,528
I feel pain when I see you unhappy.

314
00:24:05,530 --> 00:24:07,090
It's so annoying.

315
00:24:07,090 --> 00:24:09,820
I hope that you can solve my problem.

316
00:24:09,820 --> 00:24:11,840
Stop reading it.

317
00:24:11,840 --> 00:24:13,940
I remember the rest of it.

318
00:24:13,940 --> 00:24:16,860
Especially the dozen wrong words.

319
00:24:19,740 --> 00:24:24,540
But now I know, all those moments of pain or annoyance

320
00:24:25,240 --> 00:24:28,608
was because... I love you.

321
00:24:46,570 --> 00:24:49,890
Darling, don't drink anymore. Okay?

322
00:24:50,690 --> 00:24:53,690
You can read the love letter by yourself.

323
00:24:53,690 --> 00:24:56,170
Then you can drink the cross-cupped wine by yourself.

324
00:25:32,030 --> 00:25:34,096
Look at this situation.

325
00:25:54,990 --> 00:25:59,390
I won't lose this ring again.

326
00:26:00,260 --> 00:26:02,890
I won't give you a chance to.

327
00:26:08,320 --> 00:26:11,880
