328
00:26:12,580 --> 00:26:16,658
I'll be gone for a long time at this training course. You won't even see me off.

329
00:26:16,660 --> 00:26:18,540
My friends abroad will take care of you.

330
00:26:18,540 --> 00:26:21,640
Besides, you were the one who wanted to go.

331
00:26:22,340 --> 00:26:24,700
Then I won't go, okay?

332
00:26:24,700 --> 00:26:26,720
A woman's words are as untrustworthy as ghosts.

333
00:26:26,720 --> 00:26:28,900
Hurry up. You are running late.

334
00:26:28,900 --> 00:26:30,440
Listen, Qiao Musheng.

335
00:26:30,440 --> 00:26:33,340
I became your assistant to experience life for my new book.

336
00:26:33,340 --> 00:26:36,350
